## Detailed Test Categories

### 1. Core Functionality Validation

**Objective**: Verify all core VJ workflows function correctly end-to-end.

**Scenarios**:

| Scenario ID | Description | Success Criteria | Duration |
|-------------|-------------|------------------|----------|
| UAT-CORE-01 | Basic video playback and mixing | Load 4 video sources, crossfade between them, no dropped frames | 15 min |
| UAT-CORE-02 | Depth camera integration | Connect Astra, verify depth map appears, apply depth-reactive effect | 20 min |
| UAT-CORE-03 | Plugin chain building | Create 10-effect chain, save/load preset, hot-reload plugin | 25 min |
| UAT-CORE-04 | Audio reactivity | Connect audio input, beat-sync effects, verify BPM detection accuracy | 20 min |
| UAT-CORE-05 | Output mapping | Configure 3-output projection mapping with edge blending | 30 min |
| UAT-CORE-06 | DMX lighting control | Send DMX to fixture, verify chase patterns, strobe effects | 20 min |
| UAT-CORE-07 | MIDI controller mapping | Map 8 MIDI knobs to parameters, verify smooth control | 15 min |
| UAT-CORE-08 | Recording and playback | Record 5-minute performance, playback with perfect sync | 20 min |
| UAT-CORE-09 | NDI video transport | Send/receive NDI streams, verify low latency (<100ms) | 15 min |
| UAT-CORE-10 | Web remote control | Connect browser remote, control parameters via WebSocket | 15 min |

**Test Commands**:
```bash
# Launch VJLive3 with test configuration
python -m vjlive3.main --config uat_config.yaml --log-level INFO

# In separate terminal, run automated scenario triggers
python scripts/uat_scenario_runner.py --scenario UAT-CORE-01 --timeout 900
```

**Validation Checks**:
- All scenarios complete without crashes or freezes
- No "Not Responding" states during normal operation
- All UI elements render correctly on target hardware
- Audio/video sync maintained within ±2 frames
- Parameter changes apply immediately (no lag >100ms)

